data.value:
It has recently been brought to our attention that you are partaking in illegal events such as piracy, exploitation, or Malware distribution. Such actions break our Terms of Use (TOS) of Microsoft © Corporation.
As a result, we may add the following restrictions to your PC for ensuring the safety of others:
• Slowing down internet bandwidth • Moderating downloads and website interactions • Canceling various provided services such as Microsoft accounts, email, and communication • Emphasising Code of Conduct
If you ensure to continue downloading exclusive software, games, or applications, we WILL revoke internet access at your location and charge payments. We take these offensive actions seriously, and you may receive a letter in the mail from 5-8 days.
